262
00:26:52.578 --> 00:26:55.604
<i>You think God
will forgive us for what we've done?</i>

263
00:27:21.675 --> 00:27:24.007
<i>I'm tired of killin'. Ray.</i>

264
00:27:28.449 --> 00:27:32.681
<i>You think God will forgive us
for what we've done?</i>

265
00:27:32.787 --> 00:27:36.280
<i>In my state. I couldn't...
I couldn't guard a corpse.</i>

266
00:27:36.391 --> 00:27:38.882
<i>Talk all the time.</i>

267
00:27:38.994 --> 00:27:40.985
<i>You know. I'm no good at that.</i>

268
00:27:42.597 --> 00:27:45.293
<i>You know. I'm no good at that.</i>

269
00:27:46.635 --> 00:27:48.728
<i>You know how they say...</i>

270
00:27:50.806 --> 00:27:53.206
