279
00:28:55.674 --> 00:28:57.574
click. nothing.

280
00:28:57.676 --> 00:28:59.974
You're talking about a bad primer.

281
00:29:00.079 --> 00:29:02.138
Yeah. I... Yeah. Yeah. yeah.

282
00:29:02.248 --> 00:29:04.739
But I... You know. right. dimple.
Dimple on the primer.

283
00:29:04.850 --> 00:29:06.944
That may be.

284
00:29:07.053 --> 00:29:10.648
Well. like we used to say...

285
00:29:10.757 --> 00:29:14.625
