Creasy. You're smiling.

358
00:37:31.050 --> 00:37:33.645
- What?
- You were smiling.

359
00:37:33.754 --> 00:37:35.847
- No. I'm not. No. I was not.
- You were.

360
00:37:35.956 --> 00:37:38.356
- You're not now. but you were.
- You were smiling. I wasn't.

361
00:37:38.459 --> 00:37:40.256
- You were.
- When?

362
00:37:40.361 --> 00:37:42.852
- Like five seconds ago.
- I'm not smiling.

363
00:37:42.963 --> 00:37:46.490
- A second ago you were.
- You said five seconds ago. Now that's six.

364
00:37:46.600 --> 00:37:48.795
- Six seconds ago I wasn't smiling.
- Ten seconds ago.

365
00:37:48.903 --> 00:37:52.533
Ten seconds ago I was smiling. Okay. in
the next 10 seconds. let's see who smiles first.

366
00:37:57.612 --> 00:38:00.308
- You smiled already. See? You did.
- Mmm!

367
00:38:00.415 --> 00:38:02.883
- No. that wasn't a... That was a smirk.
- Yeah. you...

368
00:38:02.984 --> 00:38:05.214
That's not a smile.
A smirk is different.

369
00:38:05.320 --> 00:38:09.189
They both start with "S." but they're
not the same... Do your homework.

370
00:38:09.292 --> 00:38:11.260
You were.

371
00:38:14.430 --> 00:38:17.365
Bang!

372
00:38:17.467 --> 00:38:19.901
Stop. stop. stop. stop. stop.
Come back. come back.

373
00:38:20.002 --> 00:38:22.835
Bang!

374
00:38:22.939 --> 00:38:26.807
<i>Stop. stop. stop. stop.
stop. stop. stop. stop. Come here.</i>

375
00:38:26.909 --> 00:38:29.242
<i>Hurry up. hurry up. Set.</i>

376
00:38:29.346 --> 00:38:31.075
Bang!

377
00:38:31.181 --> 00:38:34.309
Bang!

378
00:38:35.853 --> 00:38:38.822
You don't flinch when you hear
