384
00:39:13.058 --> 00:39:15.856
Oh. I missed you so much.

385
00:39:15.961 --> 00:39:18.623
- I missed you too.
- How are you doing? I got a surprise for you.

386
00:39:18.731 --> 00:39:20.926
