- Ready?

387
00:39:21.033 --> 00:39:23.525
- Huh?
- You got me a dog! You finally got me a dog!

388
00:39:23.637 --> 00:39:27.129
<i>- Huh?
- You bought me a dog. finally! Oh. my God!</i>

389
00:39:27.240 --> 00:39:29.367
<i>- What do you think?
- Oh. my gosh.</i>

390
00:39:29.476 --> 00:39:32.445
