Bhutan.
It's a Himalayan kingdom.

394
00:39:42.990 --> 00:39:46.482
<i>They were having some problems
with their royal family not that long ago.</i>

395
00:39:46.594 --> 00:39:49.324
<i>- Mm-hmm.
- Okay.</i>

396
00:39:49.430 --> 00:39:52.627
Any more questions?

397
00:39:52.733 --> 00:39:54.633
