402
00:40:04.513 --> 00:40:07.505
Nonya. Nonya business.
That's who.

403
00:40:07.616 --> 00:40:11.848
<i>- Okay?
- Hi.</i>

404
00:40:11.954 --> 00:40:15.652
Tomorrow after you drop off Pita.
could you take me to get my hair done?

405
00:40:15.758 --> 00:40:18.488
- Yes. ma'am.
- All right.

406
00:40:18.595 --> 00:40:22.156
Well. um. I'll leave you two
