419
00:41:14.820 --> 00:41:16.754
Okay. Hey.

420
00:41:16.856 --> 00:41:20.053
I'm a prisoner in the block
until the gunshot sets me free.

421
00:41:20.159 --> 00:41:22.559
- Don't smile. don't fool around if you want to win.
- Okay.

422
00:41:22.662 --> 00:41:24.653
- You want to win? Trained or untrained?
- Trained.

423
00:41:24.764 --> 00:41:27.062
Go.

424
00:41:27.166 --> 00:41:31.604
<i>- Señor Creasy. nice to see you.
