431
00:43:28.761 --> 00:43:31.855
Well. when we were young
and he was younger...

432
00:43:31.964 --> 00:43:34.695
all heads turned our way.

433
00:43:34.802 --> 00:43:37.464
We made a deal
to take the world together.

434
00:43:37.571 --> 00:43:41.405
