I got a call. and he said...</i>

435
00:43:41.508 --> 00:43:44.807
"I'm in love! I'm in love!

436
00:43:44.912 --> 00:43:47.676
<i>And I'm moving to Mexico. "</i>

437
00:43:47.781 --> 00:43:50.147
<i>And... I said...</i>

438
00:43:50.250 --> 00:43:53.914
- "What happened to the plan?
What happened to it?"

439
00:43:54.022 --> 00:43:56.115
I said. "The plan's right here. "

440
00:43:56.224 --> 00:43:58.692
Yeah. Yeah. And what'd I do?

441
00:43:58.793 --> 00:44:01.193
I hung up. then I met Alicia...

442
00:44:01.296 --> 00:44:05.494
and then I went.
"Oh. now I got you! I got you. "

443
00:44:05.600 --> 00:44:08.330
I got it. Can I kiss her? Is that...

444
00:44:08.436 --> 00:44:12.066
Absolutely!
Hey. what are you doing?

445
00:44:17.780 --> 00:44:22.410
- You got me.
