patron saint of lost causes.

449
00:44:44.708 --> 00:44:46.539
Wow.

450
00:44:48.479 --> 00:44:50.413
Well deserved.

451
00:44:54.652 --> 00:44:57.246
Thank you. Pita. It's beautiful.

452
00:44:58.890 --> 00:45:00.790
