455
00:45:54.315 --> 00:45:56.442
Yes.

456
00:45:56.550 --> 00:45:59.782
I don't want to play piano.
I want to swim.

457
00:45:59.888 --> 00:46:02.322
It's not open for discussion.
honey. okay?

458
00:46:02.424 --> 00:46:06.292
Mr. Lozzi's a very. very famous teacher.
and if he accepts you as his student...

459
00:46:06.394 --> 00:46:08.362
you're gonna play the piano.

460
00:46:08.463 --> 00:46:10.397
Whatever.

461
00:46:10.498 --> 00:46:12.966
Baby.

462
00:46:13.068 --> 00:46:15.628
- I love you.
- I love you.

463
00:46:15.737 --> 00:46:19.139
