- Okay.

464
00:46:19.241 --> 00:46:21.232
Okay. honey.

465
00:46:31.687 --> 00:46:34.247
If you broke all my fingers.
then taped them back together...

466
00:46:34.357 --> 00:46:37.327
I wouldn't be able to play piano.
but I could still swim.

467
00:46:37.427 --> 00:46:39.759
Sam. get back.

468
00:46:39.863 --> 00:46:42.730
Don't be a crybaby.
You're tougher than that.

469
00:46:42.833 --> 00:46:45.301
<i>Sit. sit. sit. sit. sit. sit.</i>

470
00:46:47.604 --> 00:46:51.370
